_:N01d22fd12d8d4b86b1ef4b1ddafcf6e2 <http://schema.org/description> "We are “always on” – ready to fight globally across all domains to make the UK secure at home and strong abroad. Detecting threats early and responding with specialist capabilities to out-think, out-pace and out-fight our adversaries. CSOC is part of the Ministry of Defence ." .
